('ONET-TANK_CAR_TRUCK_AND_SHIP_LOADERS', 'source_onet_tank_car_truck_and_ship_loaders', 'Tank Car, Truck, and Ship Loaders', 'Tank Car, Truck, and Ship Loaders is an imported ONET role/occupation concept. It needs TALLENTIN normalization before production routing.', 'role_title', 'Load and unload chemicals and bulk solids, such as coal, sand, and grain, into or from tank cars, trucks, or ships, using material moving equipment. May perform a variety of other tasks relating to shipment of products. May gauge or sample shipping tanks and test them for leaks.', ARRAY['Barge Loader','Barges Loader','Bulk Tank Car Unloader','Car Loader','Car Unloader','Caustics Loader','Coal Dumping Equipment Operator','Dock Loader','Load Out Person','Loader','Loader Operator','Loading Operator','Oil Movements Operator','Pumper Gauger','PVC Loader (Polyvinyl Chloride Loader)','PVC Monitor (Polyvinyl Chloride Monitor)','Rail Car Loader','Rail Loader','Receiving Operator','Ship Unloader','Shipping and Receiving Operator','Shipping Loader','Ships Loader','Spout Tender','Tank Car Loader','Tank Truck Loader','Tankerman','Truck Loader','Truck Unloader','Unloader','Warehouse Associate','Warehouse Loader','Warehouse Shipping Associate','Warehouse Shipping Clerk','Warehouse Truck Loader','Warehouse Unloader']::text[], ARRAY['Tank Car, Truck, and Ship Loaders','Barge Loader','Barges Loader','Bulk Tank Car Unloader','Car Loader','Car Unloader','Caustics Loader','Coal Dumping Equipment Operator','Dock Loader','Load Out Person','Loader','Loader Operator','Loading Operator','Oil Movements Operator','Pumper Gauger','PVC Loader (Polyvinyl Chloride Loader)','PVC Monitor (Polyvinyl Chloride Monitor)','Rail Car Loader','Rail Loader','Receiving Operator','Ship Unloader','Shipping and Receiving Operator','Shipping Loader','Ships Loader','Spout Tender','Tank Car Loader']::text[], ARRAY['Reading Comprehension','Active Listening','Writing','Speaking','Mathematics','Science','Critical Thinking','Active Learning',